data.description: Welcome to your dream oasis in the serene Serengeti Estates nestled along the picturesque Caloosahatchee River. Come discover the epitome of luxury, outdoor living, natural light, and energy efficiency in this stunning 4-bed + Den, 3-bath home. Spanning 2953 SQFT the impressive La Caruna floor plan is meticulously designed by Wright Jenkins. Uncover all of the exceptional features that make it an extraordinary place to call home. Indulge in the essence of outdoor living, step out into the expansive 1.35-acre lot that offers serene lake views and unparalleled tranquility. Primary suite has luxurious spa bath, complete with walk-thru shower behind a central, free-standing soaker tub. Tile flooring throughout, providing elegant and low-maintenance living. This Smart Home is not only a marvel of luxury but also a paragon of sustainability. This energy-efficient home consumes less than 1/2 the energy of a similarly sized home, providing long-term cost savings and environmental benefits. Featuring impact windows and doors and 3-car garage gives ample storage for vehicles, while built-in storage throughout the home offers added convenience. Don't miss the opportunity to call it your own!
